in agreement with observations\nof small-scale clustering of galaxies, but is at odds with the linear\ndependence on projected separation that is often assumed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 17:32:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 12:03:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-17"}
