tication protocols. To demonstrate the feasibility of our proposal, we\npresent PakeMail, an implementation of the core idea, and discuss some of its\ncryptographic details, implemented features and efficiency aspects. We conclude\nwith some design and security considerations, followed by future lines of work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 13:46:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
