 wind calculations to the upper troposphere,\nwe find a wind structure qualitatively close to the wind observed using\ncloud-tracking techniques. Nearly simultaneous temperature and wind\nmeasurements, both in the stratosphere, are a powerful tool for future\ninvestigations of the JEO (and other planetary equatorial oscillations) and its\ntemporal evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 14:23:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 21:44:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
