tputs decay to zero for long simulations.\n  Overall, our analysis promotes multi-level LR stochastic models with memory\neffects, and hybrid models with linear dynamical core augmented by additive\nstochastic terms learned via deep learning, as a more practical, accurate, and\ncost-effective option for ocean emulation than pure deep-learning solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 07:36:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
